hej.
jag får inte igång seedningen... 
jag använder azureus och vissa av torrentarna jag gjort lades inte till automatiskt i seedningslistan. när jag försöker lägga till dessa så försöker den först ladda hem filen till en ny katalog. hjälp mig gärna!
how do i get the English subtitles to show in the movie?  they're in a separate file.
I just downloaded this and I can't play the file in ANY programs at all. It just says "file not found". Same with the subtitles file. Did this even work for anyone else?
This wont play with VLC or GOM players. Just says file not recognized. Pity, because it downloaded at an average of 700 Kbp/s..oh, well...
nothing wrong with the files. their names are just TOO LONG. open a DOS window and rename the files using their 8 character DOS filename. for more info use google.

This worked fine for me in VLC, and the English subs synced up perfect.  Like Pastafari said, the file name might be too long for windows (& mac?) users--rename them to something shorter.  Many thanks to the vid, and tomorrow I'm making gazpacho!  :3
